  92:src/voice.h   ****   // as before (every other voice). decay_ms > 0 ŌåÆ after the attack the level falls
  93:src/voice.h   ****   // to `sustain` (0..1 fraction of full; default 0 = decays to silence, a clean
  94:src/voice.h   ****   // pluck) over decay_ms. The release still applies on lift. Appended last so the
